---
title: BBQ Pork Schnitzel & Apple Slaw with Sriracha Mayo & Kūmara Fries
description: It’s that time of the week, schnitty night! This one involves tender pork, with extra flavour added right into the deliciously golden crumb. Pair it with baked kūmara fries, a sweet and crunchy slaw and a spicy mayo to hit all the right notes.
